message.entry: 裁剪矩形不与图像相交。
IMCROP 需要一个包含图像的当前图窗。
在当前坐标区中找不到图像。
IMCROP 不支持以 [max,min] 顺序指定的 'XData' 或 'YData'。

The only syntaxes supported by IMCROP in code generation are:
 [...] = IMCROP(I,RECT)
 [...] = IMCROP(X,Y,I,RECT)
 [I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)
 [X,Y,I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)

The only syntaxes supported by IMCROP with categorical inputs are:
 [...] = IMCROP(I,RECT)
 [...] = IMCROP(X,Y,I,RECT)
 [I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)
 [X,Y,I2,RECT] = IMCROP(...)
